Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时代居然连浴室都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 不要太勉强快点上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身又是血腥味 又是灰尘泥土的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有头发都脏得打结了 我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做日暮戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本只是一个再平凡不过的国中生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却遇到一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬把我拉进了这个战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量不停地涌上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我的身体也慢慢地恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身上对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 恶心死了 放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:03:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是想要抢到隐藏在我身体里面的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战国时代桔梗拥有的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在我的身体里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我又必须跟觊觎四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让自己变得更强的半妖 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去把变成碎片的四魂之玉收回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 这绝对不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从食骨之井回到现代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 不要乱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉到底怎么了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇那个时候射出去的破魔箭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射穿了妖怪的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把妖怪体内的四魂之玉射碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉的碎片已经散落在世界各处了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且根本就不知道是碎成了百片还是千片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过即使只是一个碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果落在妖力很强的妖怪手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能会酿成很大的灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来…不就是我害的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得我也有点责任…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们必须结合彼此的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把四魂之玉的所有碎片都收回来让它恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了我也是觊觎四魂之玉的坏蛋之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 现在顾不了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…我想赶快回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我根本没有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且犬夜叉又是个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你在啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了我身上还有这串讨厌的咒语念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢偷偷摸摸偷看我洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想来偷四魂之玉的碎片对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真了解我 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我不是已经说得很清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有能看到四魂之玉的戈薇的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上犬夜叉你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能集齐所有的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呀 我不是也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找到四魂之玉 我愿意跟这个讨厌的女人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你真的这么讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年前突然消失的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要先回去了 你们可别吵架哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知廉耻！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是叫你裸体！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要你穿回那套奇怪的衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我这样像桔梗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她才没关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了 这小子比初中生还幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们不能再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然以后怎么可能在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没什么不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算一个人也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？意思是没有我也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定决心了 我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家？喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我叫戈薇 我的名字不叫「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不叫臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你别走 臭丫头！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛！你阻止不了我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个四魂之玉碎片留下来给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…太不敢相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个犬夜叉 竟然从来都没有叫过我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说她突然倒下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她早上还明明很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘起来了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我出来的枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能从这里回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨头…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个枯井在我们这被称作是「食骨之井」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是丢弃妖怪尸体的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要经过几天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些亡骸就会莫名其妙地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…好像是百足妖怪的尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心 我不敢进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「发笼」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过光看得到是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那个臭女人我也落个清静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 你们想和我动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做逆发结罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你记不住也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你就快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把四魂之玉弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的碎片在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的碎片在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 那个女人怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看都是村里的女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道现在还想除掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不能伤害那些女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦 浑身是血的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能换一种说法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能伤害那些女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们想杀我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们好像被什么东西操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢？戈薇不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个讨厌的女人已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 我一个人就可以解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能对村里的这些女孩动手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在说什么梦话啊 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是差点被这些人杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你还不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不打倒在背后操纵她们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间听你啰哩叭唆那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样 犬夜叉 把头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先切断操纵那些女孩的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发？我没看见什么头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得好好抓住这边的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 快逃啊！犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵这些头发的真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这个样子就算我看不到头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用力扯 就可以拉出后面的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 差不多该做个了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬、犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有切到肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是普通人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋早就落地了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有新的啊 这样下去就没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 这里就交给我来应付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快死了就别装酷了 枫老太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的银发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我抓紧了 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要小心一点…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结实的家伙 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这漂亮的银发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非拿到不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 你刚才是不是说看到了头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就告诉我 操纵头发的妖怪在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑了 我已经伤成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有受伤 凭我的眼力也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去…找戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说那个女人看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的对手 要靠戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有戈薇…你赢不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是枯井下面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我被一个女孩袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就掉进枯井里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个古井里不是找了很多遍了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是姐姐真的进去了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是作梦看到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到我的时代了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…你这三天跑到哪去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎么穿着那身衣服啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 好可怕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆 看你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你埋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我还没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是先把你藏在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我记得的话待会会把你挖出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要忘记了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万别忘记了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候到底跑到哪去干什么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你去哪里 都不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一味地  只知道逞强的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}但是  从那时起我不再茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一定有想要与你分享的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}也有许多想向你倾诉的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论是笑容还是泪颜都想呈现给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}等待着  将曾经放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}机会重新抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}我想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}只要如此  便觉得心变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}这份渺茫的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论何时都在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}希望能够传达给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结罗操纵的头发 犬夜叉根本看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠蛮力作战的犬夜叉被不断玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解救枫婆婆 得快点解决她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么样才能够打败她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉真的能够打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称是不死身的结罗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结罗一定在什么地方有弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆发妖魔 结罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
